Список литературы для подготовки

Kitchin R. The Real-Time City? Big Data and Smart Urbanism //Big Data and Smart Urbanism (July 3, 2013). – 2013 http://diyhpl.us/~bryan/papers2/paperbot/The%20real-time%20city%3F%20Big%20data%20and%20smart%20urbanism.pdf

Foth M. Handbook of research on urban informatics: The practice and promise of the real-time city. – Information Science Reference, IGI Global, 2009. http://eprints.qut.edu.au/13308/2/c13308a.pdf

Mitchell W. J. E-topia:" urban life, Jim--but not as we know it". – the MIT Press, 2000. http://www.cies.iscte-iul.pt/linhas/linha2/sociedade_rede/pr_htdocs_network/apps/mitchell.pdf

Wigley M. Network fever //Grey Room. – 2001. – №. 04. – С. 82-122. http://isites.harvard.edu/fs/docs/icb.topic983682.files/Week%2006/W06-2%20Mark%20Wigley_Network%20Fever.pdf

McLuhan M. Understanding media: The extensions of man. – Cambridge, Mass.: MIT Press, 1994. http://monoskop.org/images/4/47/McLuhan_Marshall_Understanding_Media_The_Extensions_of_Man.pdf

Townsend A. M. Smart cities: big data, civic hackers, and the quest for a new utopia. – WW Norton & Company, 2013.

McLuhan M., Fiore Q. with Agel, J.(1967) The Medium is the Massage: An Inventory of Effects.

Shirky C. Here comes everybody: The power of organizing without organizations. – Penguin. com, 2008.

Shirky C. Cognitive surplus: Creativity and generosity in a connected age. – ePenguin, 2010. Ширки К. Включи мозги. Свободное время в эпоху интернета. М: Карьера Пресс, 2012 г.

Hagerstrand T., “Aspects of the Spatial Structure of Social Communication and the Diffusion of Information,” Papers (The Regional Science Association), 16 (1966), 27-42.

Alexander C. The timeless way of building. – Oxford University Press, 1979. – Т. 1.
